fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 advanced 66.45 points or 0.34% to settle at 19,389. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, rose 1.38% to 11.70. Bajaj Finance, HDFC Bank and State Bank of India were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The July 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 27 July 2023.
